text = 
"The crows are coming to steal your crops! Fend them off by throwing your crops at them... A little counter intuitive, I know. " +
"Each round you will purchase crops from the shop. Blue circle shows how many waves it will take for the crop to grow, and the yellow circle represents its cost. " +
"Each crop has a different ability, and that ability can be leveled up by dragging a crop from the shop of the same type onto it. " +
"Once you've started a wave, crows will start coming in from the left. Hold down click, and aim your pitchfork to throw your crops. The longer you hold, the further you throw. " +
"Be careful not to let any crows through. 20 crows get through and it's game over. How many rounds can you survive?";

